    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you may notice some minor fluid leaks and a bit of hesitation during cold starts. The exterior has several noticeable scratches and minor dents, and the interior upholstery shows significant wear from regular use. While it is roadworthy and dependable for getting from A to B, it will eventually require some maintenance to address these aging components.",
