    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my reliable ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in solid shape, well-loved, and totally ready for its next adventure! Everything runs smoothly, and it looks great inside and out. It's the perfect fit for someone who wants a dependable car that's been taken care of without that brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This FD3S chassis remains a benchmark in front-midship balance and analog feedback. Powered by the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbo rotary engine, this example maintains a linear boost curve and strong compression. The drivetrain features a precise 5-speed manual transmission paired with a factory Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery through the twisties. To address the platform's thermal challenges, a high-capacity aluminum radiator and silicone vacuum lines have been installed, significantly improving reliability. The double-wishbone suspension remains tight, providing the telepathic turn-in these cars are known for. While the finish shows minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the structural integrity and mechanical vitals are robust. A purist-spec FD ready for the canyon roads.",
      "price": 38500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 27
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean interior and exterior. Runs well. Title in hand.",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
