    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 inline-six, delivering 333 hp through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanical highlights include a fully serviced VANOS system and reinforced rear subframe mounts, addressing critical chassis longevity. The M-Variable differential lock provides exceptional corner-exit traction, complemented by a taut suspension geometry that maintains the car's signature near 50/50 weight distribution. While the aesthetics show honest wear consistent with a well-maintained driver, the powertrain remains a masterpiece of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering. A mechanically robust example ready for the circuit or the canyon.",
